</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_327" id="163r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l2"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü Weinſperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l3">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / daʒ Jr <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> cʒü den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> komen wöllet gen <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auf <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Tawb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l5">auf welıchen genanten tag vvir wöllen / doch alſo / daʒ vvir ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l6">den cʒeitlıchen vor vviſſen laſſen / . Alſo laſſen wir ewr edel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l7">wiſſen / daʒ wir die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> doſelbſthin gen <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> ſchıcken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l8">wöllen / daʒ ſie auf den Mıtwochen cʒenacht nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>frawe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l9">tag <expan>Natiuitat<ex>is</ex></expan> ſchirſt cʒü <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> ſein vnd <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> do wart </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l10">gnaden do warten ſüllen / vnd alſo mügt Jr auf den <expan>Mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l11">cʒenacht <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> des morgens auf den donerſtag 
<del rend="strikethrough">dahin </del> wie ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l12">dann 
<del rend="erased">fu</del> füglıch ıſt dahin kumen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l13">Auch als Jr vns vormals vnd <expan>yecʒu<ex>n</ex>den</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l14"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von des geleittes <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> die <expan>ſtraʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> v̈ber gewe / </ab><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l15"><expan>Laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr edel wiſſen / daʒ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nu das meiſte teil </ab><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l16">hin ab ſind / vnd wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vil mainen daʒ Jn </ab><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l17">die ſtraʒʒe v̈ber gew her auf <expan>cʒevare<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit niht füglıch </ab><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l18">ſeÿ / Doch <expan>bit<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad / wo die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des begerten / </ab><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l19">daʒ Jr ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> mit geleite <expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel </ab><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l20">vor <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd vvo etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ </ab><ab facs="#facs_327_r1l21"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Egıdıj̃</expan> Anno xj<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab></add> / vnd wo vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_327_r1l13">lıeb vnd dinſt etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_327" id="163r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü
                        Weinsperg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, daz ir
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> czü den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> komen wöllet gen
                            <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auf <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Tawb<ex>er</ex></expan> auf welichen genanten tag, wir wöllen doch,
                        also daz wir ew den czeitlichen vor wissen lassen, also lassen wir ewr edel
                        wissen, daz wir die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> doselbsthin gen
                        <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> schicken wöllen, daz sie <app><note><q type="date">auf den
                        mitwochen cze nacht nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>frawe<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>nativitat<ex>is</ex></expan></q>09.09.1411</note></app>
                        schirst czü <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> sein und
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> gnaden do warten süllen; und also mügt ir
                        auf den <expan>mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cze nacht
                        <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> des morgens <app><note><q type="date">auf den donerstag</q>10.09.1411</note></app>, wie ew dann
                        füglich ist, dahin kumen. <add>Auch als ir uns vormals und
                                    <expan>yeczu<ex>n</ex>den</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von des geleittes
                                    <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>strazze<ex>n</ex></expan> über Gewe,
                                <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr edel wissen, daz die
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nu das meiste teil hin ab sind,
                            und wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz ir vil mainen, daz in die strazze
                            über Gew her auf <expan>cze vare<ex>n</ex></expan> czü
                                    <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit niht füglich sey. Doch
                                    <expan>bit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                            gnad, wo die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des begerten, daz ir sie
                                    <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> mit geleite
                                <expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, als wir
                                    <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel vor
                                    <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Egidii</expan> anno xi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</add> Und wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dinst etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
